<p>Effective Date: 20 October 2024</p>

<p>Welcome to the QUB Music Quiz! This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our website. By accessing or using the QUB Music Quiz website, you agree to the terms of this privacy policy.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We may collect the following information to enhance your experience on the site:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Your name, email address, and university registration details when you sign up.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Details about your interactions with the site, including quiz results, pages visited, and time spent on the site.</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Information about the device you use to access the site, including IP address, browser type, and operating system.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>Your information is used to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Provide and improve the quiz experience.</li>
    <li>Track your progress and display quiz statistics.</li>
    <li>Communicate updates, announcements, or feedback.</li>
    <li>Analyze website performance to ensure smooth functionality.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. How We Share Your Information</h2>
<p>We value your privacy and will not sell or rent your personal information. However, we may share your data:</p>
<ul>
    <li>With Queen’s University Belfast for academic purposes.</li>
    <li>With third-party service providers that assist with website operations.</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations or protect the rights and safety of users.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Cookies</h2>
<p>We use cookies to enhance your experience. These small text files allow us to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Remember your preferences (e.g., quiz difficulty settings).</li>
    <li>Track website traffic and analyze usage patterns.</li>
</ul>
<p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though some features of the site may not function properly.</p>

<h2>5. Data Storage and Security</h2>
<p>We store your data securely in compliance with industry standards. While we strive to protect your information, no system is entirely foolproof. You acknowledge that any data you provide is at your own risk.</p>

<h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Request access to your personal data.</li>
    <li>Correct inaccuracies in your data.</li>
    <li>Request deletion of your account and associated data (subject to university policy).</li>
    <li>Opt-out of receiving communications by contacting us.</li>
</ul>

<h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
<p>The QUB Music Quiz website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices and encourage you to review their policies.</p>

<h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page, and your continued use of the website after changes indicates your acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

